summary:
Fashion designer with nine years experience in leading a designing process, having strong background in product management and understanding of whole product cycle. A combination of creativity with commercial goals in mind.  A bilingual in English and Russian, basic in Italian, studying Spanish.
____
To see more fashion and artistic works www.juliandrosova.com
